title: Should we reveal the Rarity System?
body:
While our initial plan was to engage the community into discovering the rarity, we did get a lot of feedback about revealing the rarity. So let's see what the community sentiment is.

FYI: THE RARITY SYSTEM IS THE HEART OF THE PROJECT

It is based on 4 layers.

• Explicit Rarity - the layer that is already revealed on the website and OpenSea

• Subrarity - the categories (e.g. How many heads based of each Epic character)

• Implicit Rarity - the most detailed rarity chart of the original artwork, all 412 variations of bgs, bodies, heads and items in the paws.

• Hidden messages - glyphs or symbols

Note: this is not a final decision vote. This is a first vote made within the community, just like the first challenge. Let's see how it goes.
